{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-tsx","path":"/HTML_01/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>HTML은 마크업 언어로, 내용에 의미를 부여하는 언어이다. 따라서 각 요소의 속성 자체를 그대로 유지하는 것이 좋다. 디자인 요소는 최대한 css에서 해결하도록 한다.</p>\n<br>\n<h2 id=\"1-기본태그-소개\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-%EA%B8%B0%EB%B3%B8%ED%83%9C%EA%B7%B8-%EC%86%8C%EA%B0%9C\" aria-label=\"1 기본태그 소개 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. 기본태그 소개</h2>\n<h3 id=\"code-classlanguage-textltpgtcode\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#code-classlanguage-textltpgtcode\" aria-label=\"code classlanguage textltpgtcode permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;p&gt;</code></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>단락을 의미, paragraph</li>\n<li>블록 요소</li>\n<li>줄바꿈을 하려면 <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;br&gt;</code>을 사용</li>\n<li>다른 블록 요소를 포함할 수 없는 유일한 블록요소이다.</li>\n</ul>\n<br>\n<h3 id=\"code-classlanguage-textltpregtltpregtcode\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#code-classlanguage-textltpregtltpregtcode\" aria-label=\"code classlanguage textltpregtltpregtcode permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;pre&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;</code></h3>\n<p>HTML 파일에 작성한 단락 모습 그대로 화면에 출력한다. 따라서 줄바꿈을 위해 <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;br&gt;</code>을 사용할 필요가 없다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>pre</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\nhello!\nhtml!\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>pre</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<br>\n<h3 id=\"code-classlanguage-textltdivgtltdivgtcode\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#code-classlanguage-textltdivgtltdivgtcode\" aria-label=\"code classlanguage textltdivgtltdivgtcode permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</code></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>특별한 의미가 없는 블록 요소</li>\n<li>블록 요소와 인라인 요소 모두를 담을 수 있는 그릇이다.</li>\n<li>콘텐트를 논리그룹으로 묶어야하는 상황, 장이나 기사와 같이 콘텐트 의미별로 구역을 나눌 떄 사용</li>\n<li>class, id를 사용하여 css를 적용</li>\n<li>문서전체 구조를 파악하는 데 큰 도움.</li>\n<li>모든 종류의 콘텐트에 무분별하게 사용하지 않는다.</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;span&gt;</code></strong> <br></p>\n<p>div처럼 의미가 없다. 하지만 인라인 요소로, 특정 콘텐트에 상세한 특성을 부여할 때 사용한다.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<br>\n<h4 id=\"팁\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%8C%81\" aria-label=\"팁 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>팁!</h4>\n<p>  이렇게 종료태그에 주석을 달아놓으면 나중에 닫는 태그를 매칭하는 데 시간을 단축할 수 있다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\">\t\t<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!--chapter1의 div--></span>\n\t<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!--chapters의 div--></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!--all-chapter의 div--></span></code></pre></div>\n<br>\n<h2 id=\"중첩목록\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A4%91%EC%B2%A9%EB%AA%A9%EB%A1%9D\" aria-label=\"중첩목록 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>중첩목록</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>ol</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>커피<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>콜라<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>ul</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n   <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>코카콜라<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n   <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>펩시<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>ul</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>ol</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<br>\n<h2 id=\"블록-요소와-인라인-요소\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%B8%94%EB%A1%9D-%EC%9A%94%EC%86%8C%EC%99%80-%EC%9D%B8%EB%9D%BC%EC%9D%B8-%EC%9A%94%EC%86%8C\" aria-label=\"블록 요소와 인라인 요소 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>블록 요소와 인라인 요소</h2>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"center\">블록 요소</th>\n<th align=\"center\">인라인 요소</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">h, p, pre, div, ol, ul, li, dt, dd</td>\n<td align=\"center\">br, a, strong, em, i, abbr</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<ul>\n<li>블록 요소는 다른 블록 요소 또는 인라인 요솔를 포함할 수 있다.</li>\n<li>블록 요소는 인라인 요소 안에 포함될 수 없다.</li>\n<li>인라인 요소는 다른 인라인 요소만 포함할 수 있다.</li>\n<li>p는 블록 요소이지만 다른 블록 요소를 포함할 수 없다.</li>\n</ul>\n<br>\n<h3 id=\"강조---code-classlanguage-textltstronggt과-ltemgtcode\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B0%95%EC%A1%B0---code-classlanguage-textltstronggt%EA%B3%BC-ltemgtcode\" aria-label=\"강조   code classlanguage textltstronggt과 ltemgtcode permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>강조 - <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;strong&gt;과 &lt;em&gt;</code></h3>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;b&gt;</code> 또는 <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;i&gt;</code>는 문서에 디자인 속성을 부여한다.</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;strong&gt;</code> 또는 <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;em&gt;</code>는 문서의 의미를 강조한다.</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;b&gt;</code> 또는 <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;i&gt;</code> 를 사용하기 보다는 문서에 의미를 부여하는 <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;strong&gt;</code> 또는 <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;em&gt;</code>을 사용하는 것이 맞다.</li>\n</ul>\n<br>\n<h3 id=\"인라인-요소---code-classlanguage-textltabbrgtcode\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%9D%B8%EB%9D%BC%EC%9D%B8-%EC%9A%94%EC%86%8C---code-classlanguage-textltabbrgtcode\" aria-label=\"인라인 요소   code classlanguage textltabbrgtcode permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>인라인 요소 - <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;abbr&gt;</code></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>약어를 의미한다.</li>\n<li>예시</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>abbr</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">title</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>World Wide Web Consortium<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>W3C<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>abbr</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<br>\n<h3 id=\"인라인-요소---code-classlanguage-textltspangtcode\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%9D%B8%EB%9D%BC%EC%9D%B8-%EC%9A%94%EC%86%8C---code-classlanguage-textltspangtcode\" aria-label=\"인라인 요소   code classlanguage textltspangtcode permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>인라인 요소 - <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;span&gt;</code></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>의미가 없음.</li>\n<li>특정 컨텐츠에 상세특성을 부여할 때 사용</li>\n<li>보통 가장 안쪽에서 쓰인다.</li>\n</ul>\n<br>\n<h3 id=\"인라인-요소---code-classlanguage-textltagtcode\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%9D%B8%EB%9D%BC%EC%9D%B8-%EC%9A%94%EC%86%8C---code-classlanguage-textltagtcode\" aria-label=\"인라인 요소   code classlanguage textltagtcode permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>인라인 요소 - <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;a&gt;</code></h3>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;a href=&quot;id값&quot;&gt;</code>\n<code class=\"language-text\">&lt;a href=&quot;#chapter1-2&quot;&gt;</code></p>\n<ul>\n<li>같은 페이지 안에서 부여한 아이디 값을 기준으로 링크를 걸 수도 있다.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- 블록 요소가 인라인 요소 내부에 있으면 안된다. --></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>a</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">href</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>dd.com<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>hello<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>a</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- h1은 블록 요소이므로 a로 감쌀 수 없다. 따라서 h1 안에 a가 들어가야한다.  --></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h1</span><sp